219
00:20:42,475 --> 00:20:43,978
[Sam]
<i>He reminded me of myself.</i>

220
00:20:44,578 --> 00:20:47,648
[rock music]

221
00:20:51,551 --> 00:20:55,957
<i>He was a freshman at St.
Gerard Academy, the youngest in his class.</i>

222
00:20:55,990 --> 00:21:00,828
<i>A dangerous combination of incredible
precociousness and hardwired pessimism.</i>

223
00:21:02,096 --> 00:21:06,433
<i>His penchant for mischief hadn't yet
become a serious cause for concern</i>

224
00:21:06,466 --> 00:21:07,902
