225
00:21:08,669 --> 00:21:10,771
<i>And though he didn't have
many friends.</i>

226
00:21:10,805 --> 00:21:13,074
<i>He seemed perfectly content
with the fact,</i>

227
00:21:13,841 --> 00:21:17,712
<i>as he said, "People are scared
of me and I like it."</i>

228
00:21:21,782 --> 00:21:25,720
