586
00:45:34,468 --> 00:45:35,369
[sighs]

587
00:45:36,570 --> 00:45:37,471
<i>Sorry.</i>

588
00:45:38,640 --> 00:45:42,042
<i>Uh, there was, uh,
a few young men who died</i>

589
00:45:42,076 --> 00:45:45,045
<i>the first week there on the
