593
00:45:56,423 --> 00:45:57,891
[Sam]
<i>Plastics?</i>

594
00:45:59,259 --> 00:46:01,929
<i>And is that... is that the work
you do now? Uh, plastics?</i>

595
00:46:02,396 --> 00:46:04,398
[Floyd]
<i>Yes. So... some plastics.</i>

596
00:46:04,965 --> 00:46:09,970
<i>Some of the work is also with,
uh, lenses. Lenses and lasers.</i>

597
00:46:12,005 --> 00:46:13,040
[Sam]
<i>Wow.</i>

598
00:46:14,308 --> 00:46:17,010
[Floyd] <i>Yeah. It's a...
